    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Restitutio facta <rs
                            key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Monks #Ordinatio #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName> per nobilissimam <rs key="#Countess">comitissam</rs>
                        <persName
                            key="#Countess #grandchildOf #Ordinatio #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Other_minor_officer #Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"
                            ref="#people/125">Matildem</persName> de quibusdam <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et <rs key="#Fisheries"
                            >piscationibus</rs> positis in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            ref="#estates/2007"><rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                            <placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                                ref="#places/2417">Quistelli</placeName></geogName>. (S.T.) In
                        nomine domini Dei eterni. Anno ad incarnatione domini nostri Iesu Christi
                        millesimo centessimo quintodecimo, quartadecima die intrante mense aprilis,
                        indictione octava. Ego Mathilda Dei gratia si quid sum, notum volo quod sit
                        tam presentibus hominibus quam futuris quod ego restituo monasterio Sancti
                        Benedicti positum iuxta Padum, ubi nunc <persName key="#Abbots #Monasteries"
                            ref="#people/2189">Albericus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preesse videtur, per hanc <rs key="#Ordinatio"
                            >cartam mee concessionis</rs>, silicet quasdam terras cum <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs> et piscationibus et <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs> quas <rs key="#grandparentOf">avus</rs> meus
                            <persName key="#grandparentOf #Marquis/duke" ref="#people/2122"
                            >Teudaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchio</rs> ipsi monasterio fecerat per cartulam
                        quam hodie in eodem monasterio habetur, quasque <rs
                            key="#Other_minor_officer">ministri</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldiones</rs> mei eidem monasterio
                        abstulerant me nesciente. Cumque <rs key="#Monks">monachi</rs> suprascripti
                        monasterii ad me venissent et michi exinde rationem petissent, tunc agnita a
                        me veritate restitui et concedi eidem monasterio omnes terras illas cum
                        paludibus et piscationibus et silvis positis in curte Quistelli, quas
                        suprascriptus Teudaldus marchio per cartam fecerat eidem monasterio ad
                        habendum in perpetuum, sicut infra hos teminos qui subtus leguntur
                        comprehenditur, sive sit meum, sive sit ipsius monasterii ex datione
                        suprascripti Teudaldi marchionis avi mei; silicet sicut exeunt fogarii de
                            <placeName key="#Canals" ref="#places/2901"><rs key="#Canals">fossa</rs>
                            que vocatur Gabiana</placeName> iuxta <placeName
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludem de Salecedo</placeName> et
                        intrant in <placeName key="#Canals">Plautanello</placeName>, et sicut exit
                            <placeName key="#Canals">fossatum novum de Plautanello</placeName> et
                        intrat in <placeName>lacum Romani</placeName>, et sicut percurrit lacum
                        Romani usque in <placeName key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludem de
                            Gardeniagula</placeName>. Quecumque vero contra hanc meam concessionem
                        ire vel infringere quoquo modo temptaverit, sciat sese compositurus eidem
                        monasterio Sancti Benedicti <rs key="#Penalty">libras centum denariorum
                            bonorum Lucensium</rs>, et insuper tacitum permanere. Actum est hoc in
                        loco <placeName ref="#places/2966">Bondeno</placeName>. Matilda Dei gratia
                        si quid est subscripsi. Signum manibus <persName key="#Witness #Judge"
                            >Othaldi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs>, <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/3517"
                            >Opizonis</persName> de Gunzacha, <persName key="#Witness">Wiberti
                            Rufi</persName> de Gunzacha, <persName key="#Witness"
                        >Amethei</persName>, <persName key="#Witness">Raginerii</persName> de Saso,
                        <persName key="#Witness #Gastaldus/vicegastaldus" ref="#people/3523">Arnulfi</persName>
                        gastaldius de Bondeno <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. </ab>
